  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "If v(t) = 3t^2 - 6t represents velocity in m/s, what is the net displacement from t = 0 to t = 4?": "如果 v(t) = 3t%2 - 6t 表示 m/s 速度,那么从 t = 0 到 t = 4 的净移位是多少?",
  "Net displacement = integral from 0 to 4 of (3t^2 - 6t) dt = [t^3 - 3t^2] from 0 to 4 = (64 - 48) - 0 = 16 meters.": "净置换=0至4(3吨2 - 6吨) dt = 0至4 (64 - 48) - 0 = 16米的零至4(3吨3 - 3吨2) = [吨3 - 3吨2] = (64 - 48) - 0 = 16米。",
  "If F'(x) = 2x + 5 and F(1) = 10, what is F(4)?": "如果F'(x)=2x+5和F(1)=10,F(4)是什么?",
