  "What is the Net Change Theorem?": "网络改变论是什么?",
  "The Net Change Theorem states integral from a to b of F'(x) dx = F(b) - F(a). It connects a rate of change function to the total (net) change in the quantity over the interval.": "净变换理论表示从 a 到 b 从 F'(x) dx = F(b) - F(a) 的有机体。它将变化率函数与间隔内数量的总(净额)变化联系起来。",
  "What is the difference between 'net displacement' and 'total distance traveled'?": "“净流离失所”和“完全距离”之间有什么区别?",
  "Net displacement = integral of v(t) dt accounts for direction (forward minus backward). Total distance = integral of |v(t)| dt counts all movement as positive. They differ when the object changes direction.": "净置换 = v(t) dt 向导账户(前向减后向)的积分。总距离 =\\\\\\ v(t)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ dt 中积分表示所有移动为正值。当对象改变方向时,它们有所不同 。",
  "What is 'net change' as opposed to 'gross change'?": "“ 净变化” 与“ 毛变化” 相比, 什么是“ 净变化” ?",
  "Net change is the algebraic sum F(b) - F(a), which can be positive or negative. Gross change sums up the absolute values of all changes, like total distance vs. displacement.": "净变化是代数总和F(b)-F(a),可以是正数,也可以是负数。 毛变化将所有变化的绝对值相加,如总距离与迁移的绝对值。",
  "What is the 'accumulation function' in this context?": "在这种情况下,“累积功能”是什么?",
  "An accumulation function F(x) = F(a) + integral from a to x of f(t) dt gives the value of quantity F at any point x, starting from its known value F(a) and adding the accumulated change.": "F(x) = F(a) + F(a) + 从f(t) dt的 x 到 f(t) dt 的 x , 从已知的 F(a) 值开始,从任何点 x 的 数量 F 值开始,加上累计变化。",
  "What is 'FTC Part 2' and how does it relate to net change?": "什么是“公平贸易委员会第二部分”,它与净变化有何关系?",
  "FTC Part 2 provides the evaluation method: find an antiderivative F and compute F(b) - F(a). This directly gives the net change in F over [a, b], which is the foundation of the Net Change Theorem.": "公平贸易委员会第二部分提供了评估方法:找到一种抗后导F,并计算F(b)-F(a),这直接使F的净变化超过[a,b],而F的净变化为[a,b],后者是网络变化理论的基础。",
  "A student's typing speed improves over a semester at rate W'(t) = 2 - 0.1t words per minute per week. If initial speed is 30 wpm, what is the speed after 10 weeks?": "学生的打字速度在一学期内提高,以W'(t) = 2 - 0.1t 字/ 分钟/ 周的速度计算。 如果初始速度为 30 wpm, 10 周后的速度是多少?",
  "W(10) = 30 + integral from 0 to 10 of (2 - 0.1t) dt = 30 + [2t - 0.05t^2] from 0 to 10 = 30 + (20 - 5) = 30 + 15 = 45 wpm.": "W(10) = 30 + 从0到10的有机体(2-0.1t) dt = 30 + [2t - 0.05t+2] 从0到10 = 30 + 30 + (20-5) = 30 + 15 = 45 湿重。"
